<Link id="l02849" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2849"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// ESP-relative offsets. Use the virtual frame pointer, VFRAME or $T0,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02850" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2850"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// instead. In frames without stack realignment, $T0 will be the CFA.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02851" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2851"><span class="doxyHighlight">      if (RegisterId(Reg) == RegisterId::ESP) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
